{"tid":1639221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"IT狗，你的資訊真的很有用","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:08.000Z","uid":88241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c08479cb046fd93282763f7bea863e3852acbd1","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人唔識做automation . 等我IT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大家點樣可以做auto<br />\n可以用黎買演唱會飛...我eason 都係咁買到既!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買演唱會飛原post <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669/page/102\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669/page/102</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教大家點樣自動 如果用chrome/firefox 既巴絲可以照住做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.去裝一個imarco 既plugin, 記住去返GOOGLE 裝</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imacros-for-chrome/cplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fimacros-for-chrome%2Fcplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp%3Fhl%3Den&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=f773164a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imacros-for-chrome/cplklnmnlbnpmjogncfgfijoopmnlemp?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1wubE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1wubE.png&h=07f270a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.裝完就會多左個icon (藍色齒輪), 再去你交費用既網頁 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8AUrYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8AUrYn.png&h=2a08cdd7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.點一下藍色齒輪去mange &gt; setting &gt; player setting &gt;改成 slow</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJOfbp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJOfbp0.png&h=05a7d1a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duz90im.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fduz90im.png&h=540e6fc2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.點一下 Record-&gt; Record Marco 就可以開始自動錄製auto script</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ex6THwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEx6THwG.png&h=044a954d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5.錄完可以按play 試一下., 無問題既話可以set max 次數就搞掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lpr8wp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpr8wp0.png&h=c2b81de5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02806db9e98967ec96f38a86c7702f608017ae56","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"95c63770e6e5fdaf2a06475c5c759a6435a6d028","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a75a5db436d4a6f07cab16ca8949d09bcfb039e2","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"00874da31faf323ca7e765d81f21dd6eb04b0408","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f0b4cbe73a8d71738a9a86abb01458f56f06f0c0","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"cdb1eb394fb8e09404015bf5bdeefa02b5210849","tid":1639221,"uid":33045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"LM!"},{"pid":"0ea3e31ed3de9746a2c403765e2b109aaaad7d66","tid":1639221,"uid":88241,"l